{"tid":47510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]俾人呃佐5萬蚊","createTime":"2016-12-20T11:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T13:14:22.000Z","uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b445d4074feed278fc62c6055df32812adefea6","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"我係一個學生, 平時有打part time<br />\n係pt識到一位同事<br />\n我借佐一萬俾佢, 因為佢話佢老婆大肚跌親急用錢睇醫生<br />\n之後佢一直冇還錢, 直到2個月後<br />\n佢話, 不如夾份開鋪<br />\n佢講佐大約得到嘅營利<br />\n我又想出到嚟可以賺到啲錢幫輕屋企<br />\n所以就信佢,答應佐<br />\n但佢話暫時冇錢, 要向大陸親戚借錢, 要我預先俾住一部份錢, $37500<br />\n係前幾日, 佢話大陸親戚會來港俾5萬人民幣<br />\n跟住今日叫我出黎拎錢<br />\n點知佢行開打電話, 等佐2個鐘都唔見佢<br />\n打佢電話叫佢上嚟, 佢又唔肯, 又唔講當時情況<br />\n白白等佐佢幾個鐘, 之後發現佢呃我<br />\n所以返到屋企, 問其他同事<br />\n發現好多人都試過借錢俾佢, 最後佢都冇還<br />\n我就確定我俾人呃佐<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點樣追返筆錢<br />\n又唔知咩證據具有法律效用<br />\n又唔知要收集咩證據<br />\n求各位巴絲打幫手<br />\n我知我蠢, 但我真係需要大家幫手, 拎返啲錢, 就算部份錢都好"},{"pid":"774e5cb6faeafccd11cbf614b36cd4fa3d9ab437","tid":47510,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"比錢佢係禁出黎出現金定過數？"},{"pid":"85773c671022196fa2db86b2778347ec2e0bd8b8","tid":47510,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"同比佢呃咗錢同事去報警,公司人事部應該有佢資料,警察好快會拉人#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"72c8a54183a86f6da904b0f6599de490685735e2","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢佢係禁出黎出現金定過數？</blockquote><br />\n大部份都係俾現金"},{"pid":"67371c100dd1a5f015f88f4ac64f15021d3fb4ec","tid":47510,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"補多句,樓豬真係好蠢,但希望你拎得返啲錢<br />\n<br />\n順便支持下肥婆icon#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"9444ef71ed5de6d8c52bffe8ac826726557958c0","tid":47510,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"睇親長文 都唔知係潮文回帶定真野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb133ee90d3e5b864f5a8fb22bc5bf7f28173a","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同比佢呃咗錢同事去報警,公司人事部應該有佢資料,警察好快會拉人undefined</blockquote><br />\n即使拉佐, 但未必拎返啲錢"},{"pid":"c79948275dee0c246eebbeb2bb22243df9edbd00","tid":47510,"uid":61803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:43:53.000Z","msg":"同樣俾人呃錢  走數撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b6891f327e2665c64a26b46c1e677c127f5f84","tid":47510,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"#[joyce]#fatc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"22d4d765ae6ec8c4bbf8b4e660fcdef6c869a5c5","tid":47510,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"入世未深<br />\n經一事蔡一智"},{"pid":"2fa0d4734404eb92ee1c1a0697736451b2009997","tid":47510,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ba1fa1f4748b1f206599950a19001f4465d359","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣俾人呃錢  走數撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇試過追佢還錢"},{"pid":"294c62650118c635f82ceb92ecc124efc3b2ad55","tid":47510,"uid":66187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"經一事蔡一智吧"},{"pid":"d1d3fe5660737f4732222ad9cda59c4765a50d48","tid":47510,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"好銀眼 肥婆"},{"pid":"860917fc791778fcdb4fc757c167585987448c58","tid":47510,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"樓主預左無㗎喇。<br />\n<br />\n佢呢啲係擺明昆9人但警察都吹佢唔脹。<br />\n<br />\n皆因所有嘢都係口講口賠"},{"pid":"d5f7a0937bf46c0764aaae276ed88c6a97a0f4fe","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主預左無㗎喇。<br />\n<br />\n佢呢啲係擺明昆9人但警察都吹佢唔脹。<br />\n<br />\n皆因所有嘢都係口講口賠</blockquote><br />\n其實有寫單據, 但唔知有冇效"},{"pid":"b3d3ed5076dc6d61eb627f65fad6c2d223c38b4c","tid":47510,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"樓主連埋其他同事報警睇下入唔入到佢罪算啦，除非揾人追佢屋企人數，如果唔係好難追返啲錢"},{"pid":"31144eb99a7eb8e721ddd304c147fcc82760db99","tid":47510,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"我借到你錢係我本事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 引新會員"},{"pid":"dc991d0841ffcbc9a22efd1ab9f0e4a4fd19feca","tid":47510,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主連埋其他同事報警睇下入唔入到佢罪算啦，除非揾人追佢屋企人數，如果唔係好難追返啲錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小額錢債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a2e6a9a9455b943f93dda5a13439d2e197d6a4","tid":47510,"uid":42218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主連埋其他同事報警睇下入唔入到佢罪算啦，除非揾人追佢屋企人數，如果唔係好難追返啲錢</blockquote><br />\n我同事睇過我手上單據, 話唔多有用規(有手寫單據, Whatsapp記錄, 有影佢同單據嘅相), 所以叫我搵多啲證據<br />\n同時問下巴絲有咩辨法"},{"pid":"bb76c73e12d4ae58a7e2858d055fabf08d8d14fa","tid":47510,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主連埋其他同事報警睇下入唔入到佢罪算啦，除非揾人追佢屋企人數，如果唔係好難追返啲錢</blockquote><br />\n我同事睇過我手上單據, 話唔多有用規(有手寫單據, Whatsapp記錄, 有影佢同單據嘅相), 所以叫我搵多啲證據<br />\n同時問下巴絲有咩辨法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫多兩三個老友，踩上佢屋企，叫佢屋企人還。還唔到都叫佢寫借據，我之前試過咁去追返比你多既數返黎，揾幾個惡fd扮收數佬。"},{"pid":"a48dfa7a7b410442f71ab28424370d9b2ca87985","tid":47510,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb41776f779f6a3753fb6de7112626f3083a0194","tid":47510,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"冇架喇<br />\n帶眼識人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e5ea8faaeac6998f0c15ee1692a3d63bee3343","tid":47510,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"認真！<br />\n<br />\n找律師陪你去報警（因為你自己去d黑警為左唔想做野會屌走你）<br />\n<br />\n然後d警犬為左唔想做野，會迫個被告還錢比你，<br />\n然後叫你講係一場誤會，然後佢地就唔撚使做，close file!"},{"pid":"f67cbf7099de4060bc161dc73ea10f7fb9eaa18e","tid":47510,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"才到光棍手⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔好咁傻仔啦！"}]}